Combos with [Ring of Thune](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ring of Thune). This card is so raunchy. I mean, it's not [Baneslayer Angel](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Baneslayer Angel) but, it can become just as large of a threat when you have tons of card draw. With **this guy** you can cantrip your whole hand or more every turn with the help of [Mentor of the Meek](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mentor of the Meek). Works well with exalted. Also, apparently works really well with [Mikaeus, The Lunarch](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mikaeus, The Lunarch) who would have guessed that it just so happens I have him in my deck anyways. [Cavern of souls](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cavern of souls) anyone?  

@AMart83 If you don't like him, you built your deck wrong. This card is a bomb in limited and a great card in constructed. It's not [Baneslayer Angel](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Baneslayer Angel) but, that card is pretty broken. This is Tier 2.  

For me, 4.5/5 and for all those fellow Johnny/Spike players out there.

